&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 17 countries, serving +8 million customers who trusted us with over 100B in assets. But we’re striving for more. But we’re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
