&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working closely with product and business stakeholders to define and build meaningful product metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing analytical products such as data models, dashboards, reports and tooling to enable self-serve reporting and analysis for stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improving our architecture (cloudbased and always evolving) based on what brings the most impact to cost reduction and speed, applying software engineering best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Taking ownership of projects from scoping to delivery and adoption, working autonomously&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
