&lt;li&gt;Experience across all stages of the data pipeline: ingestion, transformations, mart creation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with our tech stack is a bonus: S3/Snowflake/Airflow/Python/DBT&lt;/li&gt;
