&lt;p&gt;We build self-service platforms, golden paths, and opinionated tooling so that over 300 engineers can ship with confidence. From Kubernetes fleet management and CI/CD to an internal Developer Hub built on Backstage, our work underpins every trade, savings plan, and card payment that flows through the platform.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our database platform is foundational to how Trade Republic works — every trade, savings plan, and card payment touches it. As Database Platform Tech Lead, you will set the direction, own the outcomes, and guide the team building the platform layer that makes database operations self-service, automated, and reliable at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Set the database reliability standard:&lt;/strong&gt; Architect the failover mechanisms, replication topology, and recovery strategies that meet our availability targets — and own the engineering roadmap that closes the gap between where we are and the number of 9s the business requires.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive toward zero-touch operations:&lt;/strong&gt; Define what fully automated database operations look like — provisioning and scaling to zero-downtime migrations — and lead the platform work that gets us there.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the database technology strategy: &lt;/strong&gt;Define which database technology fits which problem — set the criteria for adoption, govern the portfolio, and ensure every database choice is intentional and operated with the same level of rigour.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Define the database contract with product teams: &lt;/strong&gt;Set the standards for how product engineers interact with databases — schema governance, migration patterns, connection pooling, query performance — and build the tooling that makes it effortless to get right.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the platform end to end: &lt;/strong&gt;Set the operational bar — define on-call practices and incident response standards for database failures, and hold the team to them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the direction and drive it forward: &lt;/strong&gt;Define the long-term database platform strategy, drive cross-team initiatives from kickoff to delivery, and align database infrastructure decisions with broader engineering, compliance, and cost goals.&lt;/li&gt;
